title: 285: Top 5 Shake-up, interview with safety Jessie Bates
itunes:title: 285: Top 5 Shake-up, interview with safety Jessie Bates
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks reveal the latest rumors around the league about a pick in the top 5 that would shock many (2:25). The guys also spend time breaking down the back end of the first round (19:11) and the incoming linebacker class (25:41) before they sit down with Wake Forest safety prospect Jessie Bates (34:65).
